reviewText: The video of this 2005 concert in Buenos Aires was very thorough, very well done; the video also includes a documentary about the concert, with Soledad narrating it. The concert was great, very good production values. I got more than my money's worth, and the people at the concert am sure got their money's worth from the concert.

Esta artista me impresiono realmente, es encantadora en el escenario y de un talento innegable. Soy un Colombiano orgulloso del talento que hay de mi pas, pero esto realmente trasciende toda frontera sin la necesidad de ser una fusin o algo por el estilo, muy recomendado.
